      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must replicate all physiological boundary conditions including hematocrit, temperature, and pulsatility at Gradation 5.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump experiments conducted at fixed hematocrit 35% and steady flow only. Pulsatile VAD conditions and temperature variation not replicated in bench tests. Achieved level 3."
