      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Demonstrated direct traceability from CFD QoIs to clinical hemolysis endpoints at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index (HI) is the primary QoI and maps to plasma-free hemoglobin. Traceability to clinical threshold documented but sensitivity of HI to model assumptions not fully characterized. Achieved level 3."
