      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must span the full COU operating envelope including device-specific geometry and patient-representative flow conditions at Gradation 5.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry only. Patient-specific VAD geometry and implanted operating conditions differ substantially. Geometric and hemodynamic gap not bridged. Achieved level 2."
