      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full Monte Carlo propagation of all uncertain input parameters (viscosity, density, hemolysis coefficients) through the CFD model required at Gradation 5.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed for inlet boundary conditions only. Blood rheology parameters and hemolysis power-law coefficients treated as deterministic. Partial UQ coverage insufficient for MRL 5. Achieved level 2."
    },
