      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample size sufficient to characterize inter-sample biological variability in hemolysis measurements at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump experiments used n=3 blood samples per operating point. Statistical power insufficient to characterize biological variability for Class III device acceptance. Achieved level 1."
