      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency analysis between validation experiment input parameters and COU operating conditions required at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency analysis between FDA pump bench conditions and VAD COU parameters performed. Hematocrit, rotational speed range, and fluid temperature differ between validation and COU. Achieved level 1."
